      "text": [
        ": ما مِن عبدٍ مسلم ابتلاه الله (جلّ جلاله) بمكروهٍ وصَبر إلاّ كتبَ اللهُ له أجرَ ألفِ شهيدٍ"
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.muhajir-b-ali": [
          "7. It has been narrated that one of the two (al-Baqir or al-Sadiq) (a.s) said: “Any Muslim servant, who is tried by Allah with a misfortune and bears patience, will receive the reward of one thousand martyrs.”"
        ]
      }
